{"tid":1965772,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"康怡花園25歲男子高處墮花槽送院不治","createTime":"2020-04-09T16:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T20:40:00.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4160d41b25731ef5a4b2391e3f89e209ac23e83c","tid":1965772,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T16:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uXLGXDN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuXLGXDN.jpg&h=b74b3f99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鰂魚涌康怡花園L座，今日(9日)下午5時26分，一名男子在上址高處墮下，昏迷倒臥大廈對出的花槽，男途人發現報警。救護員接報到場，將事主送院搶救，惜抵院後證實不治。警方其後接報到場，並於現場檢獲遺書，經初步調查，相信死者姓林(25歲)，從上址天台墮下，事件沒有可疑。惟死因有待驗屍後確定。據了解，死者為上址住戶。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=5aa58fa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mFAr8LC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmFAr8LC.jpg&h=9ae9e2a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmZ1dci.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmZ1dci.jpg&h=16c9501b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200409/mobile/bkn-20200409181731684-0409_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200409%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200409181731684-0409_00822_001.html&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=bd8184ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200409/mobile/bkn-20200409181731684-0409_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2bceedc208860d8869ed3cffd7c29e72f2748f04","tid":1965772,"ui